        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-pink-50 dark:bg-pink-900 rounded-2xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 text-3xl mb-4"></i>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Safety & Trust</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mt-2">
            Safety is our priority. We work to ensure trust and support between hosts and guests.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Team Section -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center">Meet the Team</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Behind this project is a passionate creator who believes in making travel more meaningful.
        </p>

        <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
          <!-- Single Member -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow hover:shadow-lg transition text-center w-64">
            <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/104523634?v=4" 
